    <h1>New Material Makes Objects Appear Invisible </h1>
  </div>
  
  <div style="float:left; width:300px;">
    <div class="by_line">Zo? Macintosh, InnovationNewsDaily Contributor</div>
    <div class="album_time">Date: 07 December 2011 Time: 09:34 AM ET</div>
  </div>
  
  <span style="float:right; padding-right:10px;">
